Titolo: Shadow Tactics: Blades of the Shogun

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Shadow Tactics: Blades of the Shogun is a stealth-oriented video game developed by Mimimi Productions and published by Daedalic Entertainment. The gameplay is similar to that of the Commandos and Desperados series. It was released on December 6, 2016 for Microsoft Windows, macOS, and Linux, and in July 2017 for PlayStation 4 and Xbox One. A standalone expansion for the game titled Aiko's Choice was released in December 2021. It has five missions on new maps but adds no new gameplay features.



Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 84
